      <p>
        <em>AgeExpectations.com is for informational purposes only and is not a substitute for professional medical advice. Content references current AAP, CDC, NIMH, and AACAP guidance. Always consult your child's pediatrician for personalized guidance.</em>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
